---
title: Chipotle BBQ Beef & Rice Bowl with Cucumber Salsa & Coriander
description: Smokey, spicy, and totally satisfying—this chipotle bowl is a flavour-packed fiesta! Tender, saucy beef meets crisp, refreshing cucumber salsa, all topped off with a sprinkle of fresh coriander for the perfect zing. It’s bold, balanced, and guaranteed to spice up your mealtime!
